<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="utf-8">
<title>HKSJ Q-Floor Atlas v0.1.0</title>
<style>
body { font-family: Georgia, "Times New Roman", serif; max-width: 960px;
       margin: 2em auto; padding: 0 1em; color: #222; line-height: 1.5; }
h1, h2 { font-weight: normal; }
table { border-collapse: collapse; margin: 1em 0; }
th, td { padding: 0.4em 0.8em; border: 1px solid #999; text-align: right; }
th { background: #eee; }
td:first-child, th:first-child { text-align: left; }
.headline { font-size: 1.2em; background: #f5f5dc; padding: 1em;
            border-left: 4px solid #888; }
img { max-width: 100%; height: auto; margin: 1em 0; }
.footnote { font-size: 0.85em; color: #666; }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<h1>HKSJ Q-Floor Atlas &mdash; v0.1.0</h1>

<p>Pairwise70 audit of HKSJ Q-floor impact in the I&sup2;=0 regime.
See <a href="https://github.com/mahmood726-cyber/hksj-q-floor-atlas">repository</a>
for the spec, pre-registration, and source code.</p>

<div class="headline">
<strong>Headline (overall, D&#x2081; pooled, n={{ overall.n }}):</strong>
median CI-width ratio (floored &divide; unfloored) = <strong>{{ "%.2f"|format(overall.median_ci_width_ratio) }}&times;</strong>
(IQR {{ "%.2f"|format(overall.q25_ci_width_ratio) }}&ndash;{{ "%.2f"|format(overall.q75_ci_width_ratio) }};
95th pct {{ "%.2f"|format(overall.p95_ci_width_ratio) }}&times;).
Significance lost in <strong>{{ "%.1f"|format(overall.pct_sig_loss) }}%</strong> of D&#x2081;.
</div>

<h2>k-stratified results</h2>
<table>
<tr><th>Stratum</th><th>n</th><th>median ratio</th><th>IQR</th><th>95th pct</th><th>% sig-loss</th></tr>
{% for r in strata %}
<tr>
  <td>{{ r.stratum }}</td>
  <td>{{ r.n }}</td>
  <td>{{ "%.2f"|format(r.median_ci_width_ratio) if r.median_ci_width_ratio == r.median_ci_width_ratio else "&mdash;" }}</td>
  <td>{{ "%.2f"|format(r.q25_ci_width_ratio) }}&ndash;{{ "%.2f"|format(r.q75_ci_width_ratio) if r.q25_ci_width_ratio == r.q25_ci_width_ratio else "&mdash;" }}</td>
  <td>{{ "%.2f"|format(r.p95_ci_width_ratio) if r.p95_ci_width_ratio == r.p95_ci_width_ratio else "&mdash;" }}</td>
  <td>{{ "%.1f"|format(r.pct_sig_loss) if r.pct_sig_loss == r.pct_sig_loss else "&mdash;" }}</td>
</tr>
{% endfor %}
</table>

<h2>CI-width ratio distribution</h2>
<img src="assets/ratio_histogram.png" alt="Histogram of CI-width ratios on log-x">

<h2>Three worked examples</h2>
{% for ex in examples %}
<h3>{{ ex.ma_id }} (k={{ ex.k }})</h3>
<img src="assets/forest_{{ loop.index0 }}.png" alt="Forest plot for {{ ex.ma_id }}">
{% endfor %}

<p class="footnote">
Generated {{ generated_at }} from atlas.csv. All values reproducible from
spec.md pre-reg + cochrane-modern-re full_method_results.parquet
(SHA-256 pinned in spec.md &sect;1.5.1). License: MIT.
</p>

</body>
</html>
